reviewText: I've owned my SP-808 for 14 years. This  DVD taught me how to use my vintage hardware very quickly (the manual is very, very dry....) The video production is very 90's, but so is the SP-808 and the information conveyed stands the test of time. If you have a SP-808 order it. There is nothing available on youtube or any online forum as comprehensive and easily conveyed as this.
